Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎\NAll set?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要去之後的派對嗎  -可能吧\N- Are you going to the after party? - Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或許我們在那見\NWell, maybe I'll see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你叫什麼  -伊茜\N- What's your name? - Issy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看到他嗎\NCan you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-吧檯邊黑白夾克的那人  -對\N- White and black jacket by the bar? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼  你幹什麼\NWhat are you doing? What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽\NMum?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你幹了什麼  -我警告過你  克裡斯申\N- What have you done? - I warned you, Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹了什麼\NWhat have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs20\b0\pos(192,165)\fn方正細等線_GBK\fad(3500,3500)}在我們死之前\N\N{\fs16}第一集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs20\b0\pos(192,165)\fn方正細等線_GBK\fad(500,500)\shad0}兩年後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什麼\NWhat you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情\NStuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能永遠不會發生  你知道嗎\NIt might never happen, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你保證嗎  -嗯\N- Do you promise? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\NOi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是給尼克生日的\NThat's for, Nick's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在想我們要慶祝什麼呢\NI wondered what we were celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝  更像是借酒澆愁吧\NCelebrating? More like drowning my sorrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶  是今天嗎\NOh, Christ. Is that today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定那是她想談的嗎\NYou sure it's what she wants to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經幾個月沒跟我說話了  突然之間\NShe's barely spoken to me for months and now, suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想敘敘舊\Nshe wants to have a catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許這樣也好\NWell, maybe it's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想調任  他們怎麼就不能\NI don't want a bloody transfer. Why can't they just give me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我個好案子  然後別來煩我了\Na decent case and leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是指對我們\NI meant for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茜  草字頭的茜\NIssy with an S.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是工作  -小三的小三\N- It's a work thing. - The other, other woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是個線人\NShe's a contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩  我開玩笑的  我最好不知道\NSean, I'm teasing. It's better that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用告訴我任何事\NYou don't need to tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我該告訴你\NMaybe I do, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什麼意思  -現在不行  我們已經遲了\N- What do you mean? - Not now. We're late as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你不跟我一起去嗎  -不  我得回趟家\N- Aren't you coming in with me? - No, I need to pop home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-海倫今天回來嗎  -對\N- Oh, is Helen coming back today? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該至少努力\NI should at least try and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人覺得我住在那裡\Nmake it look like I've been living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回見\NSee you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對\N'Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把床弄亂了  搞髒了一些盤子\N'I've unmade the bed, dirtied some dishes.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你來局裡嗎  -不  我要去克利夫頓見人\N- Are you heading in? - 'No, I'm meeting someone in Clifton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  我之前是真心的\N'Listen, I meant what I said.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  關於你的線人嗎\NWhat, about your contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於他們想跟你談調任的事\N'About them wanting to talk to you about the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣或許真的不錯\N'It really might be for the best.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會\NHow come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許這是個標誌\N'Well, maybe it's a sign
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該考慮提前退休\Nyou should be thinking of early retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也該這麼做\N'And I should too.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  你想離開警局嗎\NWhat - are you thinking about leaving the force?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  還有我妻子\N'Yeah, and my wife as well.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你確定嗎  -我想自由  漢娜\N- Are you sure? - 'I want to be free, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自由地跟你在一起\N'Free to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顧你  給你買東西\N'To..To take care of you, to buy you things,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如昂貴的威士忌\N'like, expensive bottles of scotch...'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和美麗的黑裙子\N..And beautiful black dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你喝那酒了嗎\NHave you - have you been at that bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們...\N'Hey, if we...'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩\NSean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩  你在嗎\NSean, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是肖恩  現在無法接電話\N'Hi, this is Sean. I can't take your call,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請留言\Nplease leave a message.'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有出色的履歷  漢娜\NYou've got an exemplary record, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無需再證明什麼\NYou've got nothing left to prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-漢娜  -嗯  什麼\N- Hannah? - Yeah..Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你在聽我說話嗎  -對  對\N- Are you even listening to me? - Um, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  你說這不是針對個人\NOf course. Uh, you said that it wasn't personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實不是\NWell, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道這聽上去像文職\NI know it probably sounds like a bit of a desk job,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但到了你這個年紀\Nbut at this stage of your career
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許這不是壞事\Nperhaps that isn't such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢娜\NHannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我只是在想\NSorry, erm, I was just wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你今早有肖恩的消息嗎  -沒有\N- have you heard from Sean at all this morning? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼問\NWhy do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我想他這會該回來了\NIt's just that I thought that he'd be back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪裡回來\NBack from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說他要去見線人\NHe said that he was meeting a contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他告訴你的嗎\NHe told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  今天早上\NYeah. Yeah. This morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不需要保姆  漢娜\NHe doesn't need a baby-sitter, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不不  當然不\NNo. No, no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是關注下手頭的東西吧\NLet's focus on the matter in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是肖恩  現在無法接電話\N'Hi, this is Sean. I can't take your call,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請留言\Nplease leave a message.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  謝謝  沒事\NOK, thank you, that's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有嗎  好  謝謝你們抽出時間  拜\NNo? OK. Thanks for your time, bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是肖恩  現在無法接電話\N'Hi, this is Sean. I can't take your call,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請留言\Nplease leave a message.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩  是我\NSean, erm, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  現在我擔心了  你能給我回電嗎  拜\NLook, I, I'm worried now. Will you call me back? Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美麗的黑裙子\N'..Beautiful black dresses...'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好\NHi, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾  我想問問\NSorry to bother you. Erm, I was just wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天早上是否看到\Ndid you happen to see a blue Volvo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一輛藍色沃爾沃停在店外\Nparked outside the shop this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九點過後嗎\NShortly after nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  差不多那時候\NUh, yeah, that sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是沃爾沃\NI don't know if it was a Volvo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但肯定是藍色  -你怎麼注意到的\N- but it was definitely blue. - And what made you notice it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一開始沒有  是司機引起了我的注意\NI didn't at first. It was the driver who caught my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是為什麼\NOh, what was the reason for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他站在櫥窗外好久\NHe was stood outside the window for ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯著那條裙子\Nstaring at that dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是他嗎\NIs that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我願意堵上一切他肯定會買那裙子\NI'd have bet anything he was going to come in and buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常你能看出來\NYou can usually tell the type.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那他為什麼沒買  -不知道  之後我再看時\N- So, what stopped him? - I don't know. Next time I looked,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他站在車旁  那時我才發現車是藍色\Nhe was standing by his car. That's when I noticed it was blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後他開走了嗎\NAnd, then he just drove off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不好  有輛灰色貨車擋住了我的視線\NCouldn't tell you, this grey van stopped and blocked my view,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等那車開走後  藍色的車也不見了\Nand, by the time it moved, the car was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  謝謝\NOK, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想好是否買這裙子了嗎\NHave you made up your mind on the dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方全是攝像頭\NThere are cameras all over that part of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有人能檢查一下監控嗎  -我來\N- Can someone check through the footage? - I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  瑞秋\NThanks, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬庫斯  芙蘭  達裡斯  你們去挨家挨戶問詢吧\NMarcus, Fran, Darius, will you go door to door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-行  -好\N- Sure. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要讓巡警幫忙嗎\NShould we get uniform to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不要告訴別人  可能是白忙一場\NLet's keep this to ourselves - could be a wild goose chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼要補充的嗎\NAnything you'd like to add?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利  你有空嗎\NBilly, have you got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好\NWell done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了什麼\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到那個目擊者  有點大海撈針\NFor finding that witness - bit of a needle in a haystack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是\NNot really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  漢娜  你就恰好找到了\NOh, come on, Hannah. You just happened to make a beeline
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利夫頓今早唯一看到肖恩的人嗎\Nto the one person in Clifton who noticed Sean this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然還有其他事你沒告訴我\NThere's clearly something you're not telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  比利  這無關緊要\NLeave it, Billy. It's not material.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我來這幹什麼\NSo...why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩告訴了漢娜一個線人\NSean told Hannah about a contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近一直在跟他合作\NYou've been working with him recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想如果她告訴你\NI thought it might help
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所說的  你或許能幫上忙\Nif she talked you through what he told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的線人叫伊茜\NHis contact is called Issy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\NHang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他告訴你名字了\NHe told you her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算是吧  是個意外\NUh, not exactly. It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還說什麼了\NWell, what else did he tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎沒說  但我很確信\NAlmost nothing, but I'm pretty sure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正要去見她\Nthat he was on his way to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不確定\NBut you're not certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今早提到了她\NWell, he mentioned her this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你今天早上怎麼和肖恩在一起\NBut why were you with Sean this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利\NBilly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後  我稍晚跟他聯繫時\NAnd then, when I spoke to him again, later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說要去克利夫頓見人\Nhe said that he was meeting someone in Clifton,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我們的電話就被切斷了  突然切斷\Nand then our call got cut off, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就這樣嗎  -對\N- And that's it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他最近的調查\NJust take a look through his current investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否有異常的地方\NSee if anything stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟漢娜合作\NAnd work with Hannah on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這懦夫\NYou fucking cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現身吧  你這懦夫\NShow yourselves, you fucking cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  去那邊  我負責那裡\NYeah, yeah, go and do that way. I'm gonna go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想問問你是否在這附近\NI was just wondering if you've seen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-見過一輛藍色沃爾沃  -沒有  我沒看到\N- a blue Volvo around here. - No, I ain't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是埃文和薩默塞特警局警察\NI'm from Avon and Somerset Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不好意思  -好\N- I'm sorry. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  伊茜\NOK, Issy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}輸入密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}輸入密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}一條新信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息嗎\NAny luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  我  我沒對你說實話\NLook, I... I haven't been completely straight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在肖恩失蹤的那條街上找到了這個\NI found this in the street where Sean went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼認為這是他的\NWhat makes you think it's his?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有條來自伊茜的信息\NThere's a text message from Issy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼沒告訴蒂娜\NWhy did you not tell Tina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不符合規矩  對吧  第二部手機\NWell, it's hardly regulation, is it, a second mobile phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是個刻板的監工  知道嗎\NShe's not a complete jobsworth, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是照本宣科  坐不到她那個位置\NYou don't get as far as she has by doing everything by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我該怎麼辦\NSo, what do I do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎麼辦\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  給她發信息\NWell, I don't know. Text her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我是否能找到\NSee if I can find out anything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追蹤到肖恩的線索\Nthat might help us track down Sean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能  你不能在別人的調查中\NYou can't go... You can't go blundering blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盲目地胡亂摸索  漢娜\Ninto someone else's investigation, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說我是胡亂摸索了\NWho says I'm blundering?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都不確定肖恩是否失蹤了\NWe don't know for certain if Sean is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他明早進了這門\NHe won't thank us for scaring off a contact
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會感謝我們嚇壞了線人\Nif he walks through that door tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶  比利\NFor God's sake, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茜顯然不知道肖恩失蹤了\NIssy clearly doesn't know that Sean is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以假裝是他\NI can just pretend to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定  她能給我們一些線索\NYou never know, she might give us something to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場對話沒發生過\NThis conversation never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己找死\NIt's your funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-漢娜  -你好  薩曼莎\N- Hannah. - Hello, Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒記錯日子吧\NI haven't got the wrong day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  是今天  請進\NNo, no, it's today. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好嗎  -很好  很高興見到你\N- How are you? - Very well. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也是  你看上去真美  -謝謝\N- Nice to see you too. You look very well. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂  尼克\NHappy birthday, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢娜  我不知道你被邀請了\NHannah! I didn't know you were invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想這是那種雖然被邀請\NWell, I think it was one of those invitations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但不希望你去的場合  -胡說\N- where you're not expected to show up. - Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老態龍鍾  筋疲力盡\NAncient, knackered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙胞胎讓我感覺自己老了\NThe twins make me feel my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-姑娘們讓你精力充沛嗎  -精力充沛\N- Oh, the girls full of beans? - Full of beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這或許能讓你放鬆些\NHmm, this might take the edge off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不該破費的\NYou shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不確定薩曼莎會贊同\NI'm not sure that Samantha will approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才喜歡\NAnd that is why I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近  你最近有他的消息嗎\NHave you... Have you heard from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯申嗎  他在廚房\NChristian? He's in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯申今晚來了嗎\NChristian's here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我兒子  漢娜\NHe is my son, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  我知道  只是\NWell, of course, I know that. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  你該跟他談談\NGo on, you should speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你起碼能做的\NIt's the least you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但別對他太嚴格\NBut go easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼克  那才是問題  我們總是管太鬆\NNick, that's the problem. We always did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好嗎\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有煙嗎\NGot any fags?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸以前會在你的可可米裡面藏一些\NYour dad used to hide some in your Coco Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只會找到麥片\NYou'll only find muesli in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了\NBingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你工作了嗎  -跟你有關嗎\N- Are you working? - What's it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在餐廳\NIn a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯  我學生的時候\NOh, well, that's great. I used to love waiting on tables
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-也喜歡在餐廳端盤子  -我是個洗碗工\N- when I was a student. - Yeah, I'm a dish washer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不錯\NWell, that's good too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他們能付你工資  讓你自給自足\Nas long as they're paying you enough to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-對  還讓我不惹麻煩  -我不是這個意思\N- Yeah, and keep me out of trouble. - That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下來就要問我有沒有交稅了\NYou'll be asking if I'm paying my taxes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯申\NChristian...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們對我很好\NThey're good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為你開心\NI'm pleased for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢  還在打擊小偷小販嗎\NSo, what about you? You still chasing petty criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快你就會給人開交通罰單了\NYou'll be handing out parking tickets before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幸好你買不起車\NWell, it's a good job you can't afford a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這房子不能吸煙\NThis is a no-smoking household.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交出來\NHand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在告訴大家快切蛋糕了\NI've been told to tell everyone it is time for cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正要過去\NWe're just coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這酒真不錯  克裡斯申\NThis is a great wine, Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  你能信嗎\NI know. Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克羅地亞酒  從他餐廳拿的\NIt's Croatian, from his restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店主是克羅地亞人嗎\NOh, the owner's Croatian?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是我的嗎\NAre these mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  別告訴薩曼莎\NFor God's sake, don't tell Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興看到你過得不錯\NI'm glad to know that you're doing OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在發生了那些事後\Nafter what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說在你幹的那些事後\NYou mean, after what YOU did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見鬼\NFuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找這個嗎\NYou looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...想試試猜出他的密碼\NI...thought I'd try and guess his password.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想到了\NI'm way ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這合法嗎  比利\NOh, is that legit, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告訴蒂娜了嗎\NDid you tell Tina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很有趣  知道嗎\NYou've very funny, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還為今晚打扮了一番\NI see you've dressed for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  我覺得我們需要的一切\NSo, listen, I think that everything we need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會在那台電腦上\Nwe're going to find on that laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看了哪些文件  比利\NWhich file did you go into, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先提前道歉  我做的咖啡很難喝\NI apologise in advance. I make terrible coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對肖恩有多瞭解\NHow well do you know Sean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實不瞭解\NNot at all really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說在調查東歐的販毒集團\NSaid he was investigating an Eastern European drug connection,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咨詢了我的意見\Nasked my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  那你是的專長嗎\NOh, why is that? Is that your speciality?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是的\NAllegedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我被調派到了這裡\NThat's why I was seconded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從國家犯罪調查局嗎\NUh, from the National Crime Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對\NAye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在犯調局之前你在哪\NSo, where were you before the NCA?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好別問我那些\NIt's probably better you don't ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國家安全局嗎\NSecurity services?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軍情五處\NMi5.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想  可以讓我滾蛋\NYou can tell me to piss off if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我可能會吧\NYeah, well, I might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但警察的兒子怎麼會\NBut how does the son of a police officer end up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因蓄意持毒坐牢21個月呢\Nserving 21 months for possession with intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是老黃歷了\NIt's an age-old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個...痛苦的離婚\NIt's a...painful divorce,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸組建了新家庭\NDad gets a new family,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽有了探探賬號  然後\NMum gets a Tinder account and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克裡斯申逐漸誤入歧途\N..Christian gradually falls off the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有過同樣的經歷  還有件T恤\NBeen there. Got the T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探探賬號嗎\NTinder account?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦的離婚\NPainful divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有孩子嗎\NHave you got kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  16歲\NAye. 16-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨死我了\NHates my guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹的事很硬核\NThat was pretty hardcore, what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\NWell, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為他能判個緩刑\NI thought he'd get a suspended sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一記警鐘嗎\NA wake-up call?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有肖恩  事情會糟糕很多\NIt would've been so much worse without Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他非常棒  挺身而出\NHe's been amazing. He stepped right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他每兩周去看克裡斯申一次\NHe visited Christian every couple of weeks, every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.82,0:24:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒惹麻煩吧\NStaying out of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健身了嗎\NBeen working out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.21,0:24:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不那麼無聊\NIt relieves the boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到我給你的錢了嗎\NYou get the money I sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.25,0:24:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我會還給你  -不需要\N- I'll pay you back. - No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我會的\NI-I will, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.28,0:24:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為一切\NFor everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在法庭上力挺我  為我說話\NThe way you stood by me, spoke up for me in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都會做一樣的事\NAnyone would've done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.18,0:24:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們沒有\NWell, they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.95,0:24:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的\NSeriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你適應得還行嗎\N..Are you coping all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.70,0:24:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:24:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我交了個朋友  我們在照顧對方\NI made a friend. We're looking out for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.56,0:25:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.49,0:25:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下去打算怎麼辦\N..What are you going to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.48,0:25:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.99,0:25:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼\NYou were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.76,0:25:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-算了  這能等  -不  接著說\N- Forget it, it can wait. - No, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.66,0:25:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你有什麼計劃\NI asked what your plan was.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.77,0:25:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎麼賺錢\NWhat you going to do for money?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.09,0:26:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  我都搞定了\NOh, don't worry, I'm all sorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.08,0:26:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以幫你找工作  知道嗎\NI can take care of all of that for you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.52,0:26:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要\NThere's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.40,0:26:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前跟你說的那個人\NUh, this guy I told you about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.54,0:26:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特凡  他幫我找了工作\NStefan, he's got me a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.27,0:26:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在監獄裡認識的毒販子\NA dealer guy you met inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.12,0:26:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那樣\NIt's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.87,0:26:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一家餐廳  洗盤子\NIt's in a restaurant, like, washing dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.53,0:26:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定是正經餐廳嗎\NAnd you're sure it's legit?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.67,0:26:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就會知道了\NI'll soon find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.78,0:27:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉伊納\NKrajina.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.71,0:27:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉伊納\NKrajina!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉伊納\NKrajina...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.04,0:27:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著像克羅地亞\NThat sounds Croatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚴格來說是塞爾維亞克羅地亞語  但夠近了\NSerbo-Croatian technically, but, close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.96,0:27:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是"邊界"  或差不多的意思\NIt means "Frontier," I think, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.26,0:27:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天  比利\NOh, for God's sake, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別怪我啊  肖恩的文件裡到處都是這個\NDon't shoot the messenger. This stuff is all over Sean's files.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.26,0:28:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及一遍遍出現那個詞\NAnd that word over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.15,0:28:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉伊納\NKrajina.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.29,0:28:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道這語言\NHow come you recognise the lingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.39,0:28:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我前任和他家人逃離了內戰\NMy ex and his family fled the civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.97,0:28:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他總想讓克裡斯申說那裡的話\NHe was always trying to get Christian to speak it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.80,0:28:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢\NHow about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.03,0:28:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那地方待過一陣\NOh, I spent a wee bit of time in that neck of the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.83,0:28:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,90年代嗎\NIn the '90s?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.25,0:28:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}關於什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.86,0:28:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}克拉伊納
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.25,0:29:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉搞得一團亂\NSorry about the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.62,0:29:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  多給你的\NHere, a little bit extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.85,0:29:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要  那是我的工作\NThere's no need. That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.05,0:29:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續加油\NKeep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.73,0:29:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃午飯了\NHey, lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.43,0:29:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好膽小\NWow. You're jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.17,0:29:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.52,0:29:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不會吃了你\NThey won't eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.91,0:29:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許你該脫下...\NPerhaps you should, um, take off the...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.90,0:29:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.15,0:30:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄  來坐吧\NHey, man. Come, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.56,0:30:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到飯桌  克裡斯申\NWelcome to our table, Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.05,0:30:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你第一次嗎\NIs this your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.69,0:30:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你  媽\NShame on you, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.28,0:30:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子都在這工作三個月了\NThe boy's been working here three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.54,0:30:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先確保他會留下來\NI wanted to make sure he was staying first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.20,0:30:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今往後他跟我們一起吃\NHe'll eat with us from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.36,0:30:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特凡\NStefan?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.40,0:30:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正蘭亭粗黑_GBK\fs14\pos(192,240)\bord0}停在了工業區
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.07,0:30:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正蘭亭粗黑_GBK\fs14\pos(192,240)\bord0}好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.18,0:30:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯桌上不談生意  拜託  達沃\NNot at the table, please, Davor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.05,0:30:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事發緊急\NIt's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.20,0:30:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正蘭亭粗黑_GBK\fs14\pos(192,240)\bord0}你得去處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.60,0:30:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正蘭亭粗黑_GBK\fs14\pos(192,240)\bord0}我要怎麼找到
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.28,0:30:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正蘭亭粗黑_GBK\fs14\pos(192,240)\bord0}我給你發了信息
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.03,0:30:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正蘭亭粗黑_GBK\fs14\pos(192,240)\bord0}好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.64,0:30:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fn方正蘭亭粗黑_GBK\fs14\pos(192,240)\bord0}克裡斯申  把馬鈴薯餃子給我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.37,0:30:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不說克羅地亞語\NHe doesn't speak Croatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.73,0:30:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是克羅地亞人嗎\NWhat kind of Croat are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.16,0:30:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在英國土生土長  我媽媽是英國人\NBorn and bred in the UK, I'm afraid. My mum's English.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.43,0:30:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你姓拉蒂奇\NBut your surname's Radic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.02,0:30:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  我爸好像是裡耶卡人\NYeah, my dad's from Rijeka, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.80,0:30:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祖母也是\NAh, so's my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.25,0:31:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界真小\NSmall world, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.67,0:31:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說你有個克羅地亞的紋身\NI heard you have a Croatian tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.78,0:31:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是斯特凡的主意\NIt was Stefan's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.99,0:31:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證明我們一起蹲過號子  以及我們本是同根生\NTo show the time we served together and the roots we share.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.09,0:31:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該去了\NYou should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.72,0:31:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在嗎\NNow?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.31,0:31:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  現在  帶上克裡斯申\NYes, now. And take Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.49,0:31:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他吃完\NLet him finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.49,0:31:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚點見\NSee you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.65,0:31:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.95,0:31:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs22\b1\pos(192,198)\fn方正細等線_GBK\fad(1200,1200)\shad0}兩個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.65,0:31:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-來啊  -快快快\N- Come on! - Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.84,0:31:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  你能跑多快  你能跑多快\NCome on! What you got? What you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.48,0:31:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.08,0:31:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.39,0:31:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不行了\NOh, you're losing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.80,0:31:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋\NArsehole.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.45,0:31:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-對了  你之前說得對  -什麼事\N- Yeah, you were right by the way. - About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.09,0:31:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家餐廳\NThe restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.11,0:31:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是什麼事的幌子\NIt's definitely a front for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.25,0:31:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  你覺得是毒品嗎\NSeriously? You think it's drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.91,0:32:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還可能是什麼\NWhat else would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.84,0:32:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這家人不是我們的關注重點  肯定是小打小鬧\NThe family's not on our radar, must be pretty small-scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.40,0:32:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我看到的不是\NNot from what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.48,0:32:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都有現金\NThere's cash everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.60,0:32:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  趕緊離開那裡\NSo...get the hell out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.01,0:32:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我要留下\NNo. I'm staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.13,0:32:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別犯傻\NDon't be an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.07,0:32:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你負擔不起再趟一次那種渾水了\NYou can't afford to get mixed up with that shit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.96,0:32:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會的\NI won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.04,0:32:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我想也許  -也許什麼\N- I thought maybe... - Maybe what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.77,0:32:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以給你信息\NI could feed you information.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.42,0:32:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.63,0:32:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於他們的計劃\NAbout what they're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.09,0:32:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你調查  拿下他們\NHelp you investigate, take them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.39,0:32:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不行\NNo fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.08,0:32:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幾乎是家人  這樣不道德\NYou're practically family. It would be totally unethical.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.84,0:32:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至不合法\NIllegal even.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.56,0:32:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  他們不知道我能聽懂克羅地亞語\NLook, they don't know I understand Croatian,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.25,0:32:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我可以偷聽  匯報給你\Nso I could listen in, report back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.11,0:32:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們開始相信我了\NThey're starting to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.56,0:32:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個爛主意\NIt's a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.86,0:33:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.35,0:33:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能有危險\NIt could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.11,0:33:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想證明什麼\NWhat are you trying to prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.47,0:33:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒想證明任何事\NI'm not trying to prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.53,0:33:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為漢娜嗎\NIs this about Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.95,0:33:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.09,0:33:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-果凍娃娃  -對\N- Jelly Tots? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.37,0:33:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果凍娃娃怎麼了\NWhat's wrong with Jelly Tots?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.50,0:33:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  只是...  -喂\N- No, it's just... - Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.50,0:33:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的髒手拿開\NYou keep your grubby hands off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.56,0:33:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來這幹什麼\NSo, what we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.15,0:33:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要幫我找一輛車\NYou're helping me recover a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.67,0:33:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼車\NWhat kind of car?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要消失的那種\NThe kind that needs to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.84,0:33:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.27,0:34:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問題真多\NYou ask a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.04,0:34:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說過會教我訣竅\NYou said you'd show me the ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.46,0:34:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個傢伙  他在惹麻煩\NThere's a guy, he was causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.50,0:34:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人\NWhich guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.24,0:34:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開這輛車  跟著我\NYou drive this one. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.61,0:34:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}你很安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.09,0:34:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}在棄車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.16,0:34:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}回復
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.90,0:34:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}藍色沃爾沃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.84,0:35:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄  怎麼了  老兄\NHey, man. What's up, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.82,0:35:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那人怎麼了  -消失了\N- What happened to the guy? - Gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.18,0:35:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車走茶涼  什麼都沒了\NThe car's gone, he's gone, it's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.68,0:35:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.96,0:35:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶\NOh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.64,0:35:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  老兄\NWhat's up, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.72,0:35:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這太瘋狂了\NThis is mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.01,0:35:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.08,0:36:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了結他\NFinish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.40,0:37:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}藍色沃爾沃沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.31,0:37:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.14,0:38:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}我需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.50,0:38:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}肖恩失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.83,0:38:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}布里斯托機場
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.52,0:38:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要跟你談談\NI need to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.81,0:38:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在跟伊茜聯絡  肖恩的線人\NI'm in touch with Issy, Sean's contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.53,0:38:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會\NHow on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.43,0:38:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在店外的街上找到了這部手機\NI found this phone in the street outside the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.66,0:38:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前怎麼沒告訴我\NWhy didn't you tell me before?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.84,0:38:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在告訴你了  他在用這個聯繫她\NI'm telling you now. He's been using it to communicate with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.05,0:39:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是嗎\NAnd so have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.96,0:39:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道我不是肖恩\NShe knows that I'm not Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.33,0:39:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茜是我們唯一的線索\NIssy was all we had to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.68,0:39:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.51,0:39:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來肖恩確實在監控這地方\NLooks like Sean has definitely had this place under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.55,0:39:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去那吃過飯  在克利夫頓\NI've eaten there. It's in Clifton.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.72,0:39:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在等什麼\NSo, what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.09,0:39:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\NHang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.52,0:39:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我們沒有搜查令  -或合理理由\N- We don't have a warrant. - Or reasonable grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.70,0:39:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你肯定伊茜在那裡工作\NBut you definitely think that Issy works there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.28,0:39:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道肖恩在調查那裡\NI only know it's on Sean's radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.63,0:39:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我們該去看看\NMaybe we should take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.48,0:39:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們剛收到電話\NWe've just had a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.54,0:39:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個被毒打的男人符合肖恩的外貌\NThere's a badly beaten man that fits Sean's description.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.81,0:39:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-在哪  -曼迪普斯\N- Where? - The Mendips.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.51,0:39:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那地方封鎖  趕緊\NI want the site locked down - now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.45,0:40:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  喝點水\NCome on, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.87,0:40:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來點\NAgain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.24,0:40:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  -喂\N- Hello? - Um, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.96,0:40:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫漢娜  我是肖恩的同事\NMy name is Hannah, I'm a colleague of Sean's.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.78,0:40:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我需要跟他談談  我能跟他說話嗎  -好\N- I need to speak to him. Can I speak to him? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.08,0:40:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩  是我  漢娜\NSean, it's me, it's Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.95,0:40:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是漢娜\NIt's Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.17,0:40:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  你得堅持住  我們很快就到\NListen, you've got to hold on. We're minutes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.74,0:41:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茜\NIssy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.31,0:41:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  沒事\NYeah, it's OK. It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.39,0:41:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道伊茜\NI know about Issy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.90,0:41:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得堅強點\NYou've got to be strong now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.98,0:41:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持住  堅持住  肖恩  堅持住\NJust hang on, just hang on, Sean. Please, stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.56,0:41:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們快到了\NWe're nearly there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.50,0:41:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.93,0:41:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩\NSean.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.44,0:41:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖恩  肖恩\NSean? Sean!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.76,0:42:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武裝警察  快出來\NArmed police! Show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.60,0:42:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-安全  -安全\N- Clear. - Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.45,0:42:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  挺住\NCome on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.94,0:43:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\NCopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.15,0:43:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗找到了肖恩的腳印\NThe dogs have found Sean's trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.84,0:43:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他從西邊過來\NHe came from the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.97,0:43:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槍手呢\NAnd the shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.82,0:43:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的腳印到處都是\NHis tracks are all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.35,0:43:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後突然間  他轉身徑直朝這邊過來\Nuntil he suddenly turns and walks straight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.68,0:43:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他看到了什麼\NWell, maybe he saw something?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.60,0:43:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或有人告訴他去哪裡找人\NOr maybe someone told him where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.99,0:43:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}肖恩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.64,0:43:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}新消息  來自伊茜
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.30,0:44:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.90,0:44:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}幫我找出
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.23,0:44:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}幹這事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.76,0:44:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}我不信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.10,0:44:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}你不認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.68,0:44:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道  我們的一位同事失蹤了\NAs you know, one of our colleagues has been missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.79,0:44:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遺憾通知各位\Nand I regret to inform you that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.14,0:44:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們失去了肖恩·哈達克\Ntoday we've lost Sean Hardacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.55,0:44:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這起案件現已成為謀殺案\NThis is now a murder investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.23,0:44:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會盡全力\Nand we will do everything in our power
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.73,0:44:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到兇手  或兇手們  將其繩之於法\Nto bring the killer, or killers, to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.74,0:45:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢娜\NHannah...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.92,0:45:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得告訴你一些事\N..We have to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.36,0:45:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我們中有內鬼\NWe believe we have a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.53,0:45:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}麥當娜紅酒餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.13,0:46:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}我願意為肖恩復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.31,0:46:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}我會讓他們
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.04,0:46:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}付出代價
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.64,0:46:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1\shad1}發送


